{"tid":2085191,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當年今日：彭定康告別港督府","createTime":"2020-06-29T17:33:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T07:54:49.000Z","uid":53844,"like":240,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"fb43e9821be357cff7779fc650260e17ca92fc8b","tid":2085191,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:33:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivoAJD4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivoAJD4.jpg&h=2b45ca5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1997年6月30號，在香港主權移交的前一天。<br />\n<br />\n港督府前的英國國旗緩緩降下。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國慣例，每一位港督離任時，都會在港督府前舉行降旗儀式。<br />\n<br />\n但是這一次不同：永遠不會有另一面英國國旗從這裏升起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0uWq5Ro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0uWq5Ro.jpg&h=f54993d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在港督府，彭定康心有不甘地接過被撤下來的英國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4zwgZo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4zwgZo.jpg&h=0e830398&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n告別儀式上的彭定康一家，妻女淚流滿面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF0jqSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF0jqSY.jpg&h=fdb80e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭定康坐着皇家標誌的黑色「勞斯萊斯」Rolls Royce最後一次離開港督府。<br />\n<br />\n傳統上，港督卸任時，會乘坐坐駕在港督府前的行車路繞圈三周，表示將來必將重臨舊地，但彭定康的坐駕只繞圈兩周就離開。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fsOH7Y0RTs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfsOH7Y0RTs8&d=BZN1wbl1lFElyj%2BXlEN3CPilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=6af01cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fsOH7Y0RTs8</a>"},{"pid":"ee1fbd4e7c30f686946ef175c7f24f7f2e76877a","tid":2085191,"uid":88134,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:33:57.000Z","msg":"肥彭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498045810c1bcb74e10c5d0ce7926a210ef32e0b","tid":2085191,"uid":34119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272426c7560083288541c204688286f167009e93","tid":2085191,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:35:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137ed0a790e727826ba591ca4c096fe1c276baec","tid":2085191,"uid":154486,"like":121,"dislike":6,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"架車兜左3個圈<br />\n意思係佢會再番黎<br />\n<br />\n到時希望佢可以以國賓身份正式訪港"},{"pid":"685570e5178f1383591ae65766537a0e2c4cbdc0","tid":2085191,"uid":101537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"6月30<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730ff7fb52b2a5a9e2bdc60e80f3a0eab46fbead","tid":2085191,"uid":105176,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"Highland Cathedral"},{"pid":"d682368368f415bc3cdfc9281dcec21ce1f9e11b","tid":2085191,"uid":47091,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"137ed0a790e727826ba591ca4c096fe1c276baec","tid":2085191,"uid":154486,"like":121,"dislike":6,"score":115,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:36:13.000Z","msg":"架車兜左3個圈<br />\n意思係佢會再番黎<br />\n<br />\n到時希望佢可以以國賓身份正式訪港"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"但彭定康的坐駕只繞圈兩周就離開"},{"pid":"5e87c5c459c94cbeb69dcf215c90b113044d96e0","tid":2085191,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:41:30.000Z","msg":"Motherland <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b87427583844284d6b7c968f41b46fce92eafb","tid":2085191